                                    <foreign xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xml:lang="cu">ѣ</foreign> at the etymological place <foreign xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xml:lang="cu">з</foreign> and <foreign xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xml:lang="cu">ы</foreign> too.</langNote>
                        </scribeLang>
